WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.470
Hey, good morning family. How have you all been

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:04.550
doing? I had a dream. There was this

00:00:04.560 --> 00:00:08.629
blonde lady wearing a red shirt

00:00:08.639 --> 00:00:11.830
with blue denim shorts. She had

00:00:11.830 --> 00:00:11.840
bleach-blonde

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:13.830
hair to right here,

00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:16.710
and she looked like

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:19.109
a weather lady,

00:00:19.119 --> 00:00:20.870
the way

00:00:20.880 --> 00:00:23.269
she was describing

00:00:23.269 --> 00:00:23.279
things.

00:00:23.279 --> 00:00:26.390
Everything was green

00:00:26.390 --> 00:00:26.400
and

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:29.349
lush. The sky was so

00:00:29.359 --> 00:00:32.709
blue in the dream.

00:00:32.709 --> 00:00:32.719
Suddenly,

00:00:32.719 --> 00:00:35.270
she started pointing out that

00:00:35.280 --> 00:00:38.110
a weather change was coming.

00:00:38.120 --> 00:00:41.030
Out of nowhere—nobody was

00:00:41.040 --> 00:00:43.750
expecting

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:47.069
this—a

00:00:49.079 --> 00:00:54.389
massive dark gray cloud came in

00:00:54.399 --> 00:00:58.349
from the north, and it became instantaneously cold.

00:00:58.359 --> 00:01:00.310
Like I said, she

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:02.549
was wearing shorts and

00:01:02.559 --> 00:01:05.990
a red shirt, which I believe

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.830
represented the United

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:10.630
States because she had on red, white, and

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:12.149
blue.

00:01:15.320 --> 00:01:18.270
She pointed

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:24.230
out four massive oak trees.

00:01:24.240 --> 00:01:26.830
Each oak tree was

00:01:26.830 --> 00:01:26.840
humongous—huge

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:30.710
oak trees with

00:01:30.720 --> 00:01:33.190
beautiful limbs. These trees

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:35.270
were like

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:37.429
they were out of a cartoon; they

00:01:37.439 --> 00:01:39.830
were beautiful oak trees.

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:41.990
When everything was green, these

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:45.190
trees were full of leaves

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.670
and looked really healthy.

00:01:47.680 --> 00:01:49.350
There were four of them, and

00:01:49.350 --> 00:01:49.360
each

00:01:49.360 --> 00:01:51.510
one

00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:55.590
looked the same.

00:01:58.159 --> 00:02:01.670
When this massive gray

00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:04.950
storm came in, the air became so cold because

00:02:04.950 --> 00:02:04.960
nobody

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:09.190
had

00:02:09.190 --> 00:02:09.200
prepared;

00:02:09.200 --> 00:02:11.510
they didn't realize it

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:14.390
was about to become so cold outside.

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:16.470
That cold air

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:19.350
blew all the leaves and

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:21.670
everything off of the trees. Then

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:24.910
the dream went to

00:02:24.920 --> 00:02:27.830
black and white, and

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:29.470
the

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:32.869
