00:02:32.879 --> 00:02:38.390
Lord pointed out: one, two, three, four.

00:02:38.400 --> 00:02:41.350
He said, 'You've asked me about how

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:43.390
long the crash will

00:02:43.400 --> 00:02:48.470
last, and I'm telling you: one, two,

00:02:48.480 --> 00:02:51.110
three,

00:02:51.110 --> 00:02:51.120
four.'The

00:02:51.120 --> 00:02:53.509
first year wasn't as

00:02:53.519 --> 00:02:55.110
bad;

00:02:55.120 --> 00:02:57.350
the oak tree didn't act like it

00:02:57.360 --> 00:02:59.910
