00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:09.589
freaking out. There was no food.

00:03:09.589 --> 00:03:09.599
Suddenly,

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:11.830
I could see in the

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:14.070
dream that there was no food and no

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:16.390
preparation because

00:03:16.400 --> 00:03:18.949
people hadn't prepared while everything

00:03:18.959 --> 00:03:21.990
was green and perfect.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:27.990
People

00:03:33.440 --> 00:03:36.710
