00:03:43.519 --> 00:03:46.390
people were used to it.

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:53.030
After living through it for a couple

00:03:53.040 --> 00:03:55.430
of years, it wasn't as much of a shock

00:03:55.430 --> 00:03:55.440
to

00:03:55.440 --> 00:03:56.630
the

00:03:56.640 --> 00:03:58.869
system.

00:04:05.599 --> 00:04:08.309
The two massive oaks in the middle were

00:04:08.319 --> 00:04:11.670
