00:04:55.270 --> 00:04:55.280
220-volt

00:04:55.280 --> 00:04:57.909
plug, not a 110 like we use in the United States.

00:04:57.919 --> 00:05:02.310
This represents the

00:05:02.320 --> 00:05:04.950
wattage or

00:05:04.960 --> 00:05:07.909
